magical_brewery:tome_chapter_potency_plus.title=Potency +
magical_brewery:tome_chapter_potency_plus.body=Purified Glowstone dust can be brewed with a base potion to make potions far more potent.\nA few examples include:\n\nInstant Health -> Instant Health III\nSwiftness -> Swiftness III (1:30)\nRegeneration -> Regeneration III (0:22)\n\nSo far, I haven't come across any side effects. 

magical_brewery:tome_chapter_duration_plus.title=Duration +
magical_brewery:tome_chapter_duration_plus.body=Purified Redstone dust can be brewed with a base potion to make potions last far longer than non-purified potions.\nA few examples include:\n\nFire Resistance -> Fire Resistance (15:00)\nSwiftness -> Swiftness (15:00)\nRegeneration -> Regeneration (3:30)\n\nSo far, I haven't come across any side effects.

